{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide funding for additional policing of road traffic offences.",
        "additional_details": "We want the Government to increase funds for policing specific to road traffic  offences, as it is an area that has long been out of control, causing Police to turn a blind eye for many years.\r\n\r\nCyclists and scooter users are causing a continuous pedestrian safety concern for people on the footpath, especially vulnerable/elderly and blind people.",
        "background": "Create funding for additional Police Capacity and training for police officers to maximise enforcement of the law on road traffic offences.\r\n\r\nPavement cycling and scooter riding is putting pedestrians at risk.",
